How to use crack:
.the keygen is located in the CD in the folder "crack"
.after installing autocad, go to the Help tab and click on "about"
.then click on the button that says "Product Information"
.click on the button "Activate..."
.make sure it says "Activate the product" then click "next"
.copy and paste the request code into the keygen and enter the generated activation code
